    "description": "Sunteck Realty, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Real Estate Agent for our Patna operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Sunteck Realty:\nSunteck Realty is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct land acquisition due diligence and feasibility studies\n• Provide advisory services on property investment and market trends\n• Source and close property deals with prospective buyers and investors\n• Coordinate with architects, contractors, and project teams\n• Build relationships with channel partners and brokers\n• Manage relationships with existing customers post-purchase\n• Coordinate with legal teams for documentation and title verification\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Contract Management\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in Negotiation Skills\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Title Search\n• Proficiency in Property Valuation\n• Proficiency in Investment Analysis\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Referral bonus program\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Learning & development budget\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Patna, Bihar, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Sunteck Realty!",
